<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900727-0079</DOCNO><DOCID>900727-0079.</DOCID><HL>   Business Brief -- H.H. Robertson Co.:   Company to Change Name   To Robertson-Ceco Corp.</HL><DATE>07/27/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7A</SO><CO>   RHH</CO><LP>   H.H. Robertson Co. said it will change its name toRobertson-Ceco Corp. following the proposed acquisition ofCeco Industries Inc., Oakbrook Terrace, Ill.   Headquarters will remain in Pittsburgh, Robertson said.</LP><TEXT>   Robertson has agreed to pay $15 million plus 3.4 millionto 4.1 million of its common shares for Ceco, and to assume$85 million of Ceco debt.   Robertson is a building-products concern. Cecomanufactures doors, metal buildings and roofing systems, andit provides concrete-forming services.</TEXT></DOC>